text: Theodoros I may refer to: * Patriarch Theodore I of Alexandria, Greek Patriarch of Alexandria in 607–609 * Theodore I of Constantinople, Ecumenical Patriarch in 677–679 * Pope Theodoros I of Alexandria, ruled in 730–742 * Theodore I Laskaris, Emperor of Nicaea in 1204–1221 or 1205–1222
title: Theodoros I
